ng%20Willy%20Wonka%20(left).%20The%20House%20of%20Illuminati's%20%26quot%3BWilly's%20Chocolate%20Experience%26quot%3B%20(right)%20in%20Glasgow%2C%20Scotland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e01df4ce7f1785b2e4d128%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20three%20Willy%20Wonkas%20but%20I%20was%20the%20most%20unlucky%20because%20I%20went%20first%20and%20stayed%20for%20three%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20doing%20it%20through%20either%20commitment%20or%20stupidity%2C%26quot%3B%20actor%20Paul%20Connell%20(not%20pictured)%20told%20The%20Independent.%3Cp%3ESilver%20Screen%20Collection%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Stuart%20Sinclair%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EActor%20and%20stand-up%20comedian%2C%20Paul%20Connell%20was%20hired%20to%20play%20Willy%20Wonka%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Scotland.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Wonka-themed%20event%20was%20reviled%20by%20attendees%20for%20its%20low%20production%20value.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EConnell%20said%20he%20thought%20he%20was%20losing%20his%20mind%20after%20playing%20Wonka%20over%20three%20hours%20straight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20actor%20who%20played%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstars-of-willy-wonka-and-the-chocolate-factory-where-are-they-now%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWilly%20Wonka%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20chocolate-factory-themed%20event%20in%20Scotland%20says%20he%20had%20such%20a%20bad%20time%20at%20the%20gig%20he%20felt%20like%20he%20was%20losing%20his%20mind.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Connell%2C%2031%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fhome-news%2Fwilly-wonka-experience-glasgow-chocolate-event-b2504464.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20Thursday%20report%20that%20he%20worked%20at%20the%20House%20of%20Illuminati's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fac