e's%20Opposition%20party%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20deduced%20the%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%20no%20longer%20trusted%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20yesterday%20questioned%20whether%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20just%2025%20MLAs%2C%20was%20working%20overtime%20to%20overthrow%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinus%20the%20six%20disqualified%20MLAs%2C%20the%20Congress%20now%20has%2034%20MLAs%20in%20the%2062-member%20house.%20Three%20independent%20MLAs%20who%20supported%20the%20Congress%20also%20cross-voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20democracy%2C%20the%20public%20has%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20the%20government%20of%20their%20choice.%20The%20people%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20used%20this%20right%20and%20formed%20the%20Congress%20government%20with%20a%20clear%20majority.%20But%20BJP%20wants%20to%20crush%20this%20right%20of%20the%20people%20by%20misusing%20money%20power%2C%20power%20of%20agencies%20and%20power%20of%20the%20Centre%2C%26quot%3B%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20the%20microblogging%20platform%20X%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709190180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fr8crplic_himachal-pradesh-chief-minister-sukhvinder-singh-sukhu-ani_625x300_28_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-congress-mlas-who-cross-voted-in-favour-of-bjp-in-himachal-pradesh-rajya-sabha-polls-disqualified-5148484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Six%20Congress%20MLAs%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20who%20cross-voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20have%20been%20disqualified%20from%20the%20assembly%2C%20the%20Speaker%20announced%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-congress-mla