20his%20veins%20for%20a%20lethal%20injection%2C%20leaving%20time%20for%20his%20death%20warrant%20to%20expire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Idaho%20Maximum%20Security%20Institution%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e01db26080194819fb18f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222037%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECreech%20was%20to%20be%20executed%20at%20the%20Idaho%20Maximum%20Security%20Institution.%3Cp%3ESarah%20A.%20Miller%2FFor%20ProPublica%2FTribune%20News%20Service%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThomas%20Creech%2C%2073%2C%20had%20his%20execution%20stopped%20because%20the%20medical%20team%20couldn't%20find%20a%20vein%20to%20administer%20a%20lethal%20injection.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOfficials%20said%20they%20would%20let%20his%20death%20warrant%20expire%20at%2011%3A59%20p.m.%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECreech%20is%20convicted%20of%20five%20murders%20and%20has%20been%20on%20death%20row%20for%2043%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIdaho%20officials%20stopped%20the%20execution%20of%20a%2073-year-old%20convicted%20serial%20killer%20after%20the%20medical%20team%20couldn't%20find%20his%20veins%20for%20a%20lethal%20injection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20Creech%2C%20who%20was%20imprisoned%20in%201974%20and%20has%20been%20convicted%20of%20five%20murders%20in%20three%20states%2C%20was%20to%20be%20executed%20in%20Idaho%20Maximum%20Security%20Institution%20at%2010%20a.m.%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idoc.idaho.gov%2Fcontent%2Fnews%2Fexecution-updates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20the%20state's%20corrections%20department.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20around%2011%20a.m.%2C%20Corrections%20Director%20Josh%20Tewalt%20announced%20that%20the%20execution%20could%20not%20proceed%20because%20the%20medical%20team%20was%20unable%20to%20establish%20an%20IV%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreech%20was%20returned%20to%20his%20cell%2C%20and%20his%20death%20warrant%20was%20set%20to%20expire%20that%20day%20at%2011%3A59%20p.m.%2C%20per%20the%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2dSjxk33Xng%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20conference%20held%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20noon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tewalt%20said%20three%20medical%20professionals%20made%20a%20combined%20eight%20attempts%20to%20find%20Creech's%20veins%20for%20an%20IV%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20tried%20his%20right%20arm%2C%20then%20his%20right%20leg%2C%20then%20his%20left%20arm%2C%20then%20his%20left%20leg%2C%20but%20were%20ultimately%20unsuccessful%2C%20Tewalt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20planning%20to%20allow%20the%20death%20warrant%20to%20expire%20because%20we%20don't%20anticipate%20a%20change%20in%20status%20or%20circumstance%20that%20would%20allow%20us%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20execution%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Tewalt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutions%20in%20Idaho%20are%20rare.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idoc.idaho.gov%2Fcontent%2Fprisons%2Fdeath-row%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20state%20has%20eight%20inmates%20on%20death%20row%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20the%20some%202%2C300%20people%20with%20death%20sentences%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreech's%20defense%20attorneys%2C%20from%20the%20Federal%20Defender%20Services%20of%20Idaho%2C%20criticized%20the%20corrections%20department%20for%20what%20they%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bbotched%26quot%3B%20execution%2C%20per%20the%20local%20paper%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idahostatesman.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fcrime%2Farticle286035906.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIdaho%20Statesman.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20precisely%20the%20kind%20of%20mishap%20we%20warned%20the%20state%20and%20the%20courts%20would%20happen%20when%20attempting%20to%20execute%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20oldest%20death-row%20inmates%20in%20circumstances%20completely%20shielded%20in%20secrecy%20despite%20a%20well-known%20history%20of%20getting%20drugs%20from%20shady%20sources%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Deborah%20A.%20Czuba%2C%20a%20lawyer%20on%20the%20Federal%20Defender%20Services%20of%20Idaho's%20unit%20concerning%20death-row%20cases%2C%20per%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Tewalt%20said%20the%20halting%20of%20Creech's%20execution%20showed%20that%20the%20system%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20are%20characterizing%20today's%20events%20as%20a%20failure%2C%20but%20the%20opposite%20is%20true.%20The%20process%20worked%20to%20prevent%20a%20failure%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20an%20important%20distinction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idoc.idaho.gov%2Fcontent%2Fnews%2Fexecution-updates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%20on%20his%20department's%20website.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETewalt%20said%20authorities%20are%20discussing%20an%20execution%20by%20firing%20squad%2C%20but%20are%20struggling%20to%20find%20units%20or%20contractors%20willing%20to%20carry%20out%20such%20a%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECreech's%20history%20with%20murder%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20he%20says%20is%20a%20life%20reversal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECreech%20grew%20up%20in%20Ohio%20but%20has%20been%20serving%20his%20sentences%20in%20Idaho%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20there%20in%201974.%20He%20has%20been%20convicted%20of%20three%20murders%20in%20Idaho%2C%20one%20in%20California%2C%20and%20one%20in%20Oregon%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadacounty.id.gov%2Fprosecutor%2Fpress-releases%2Fada-county-prosecutors-office-statement-following-thomas-creechs-commutation-hearing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20the%20Ada%20County%20Prosecutor's%20Office.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20death%20sentence%20was%20commuted%20to%20life%20imprisonment%2C%20but%20he%20was%20put%20on%20death%20row%20again%20in%201983%20after%20beating%20a%2022-year-old%20inmate%20to%20death.%20Prosecutors%20said%20he%20killed%20his%20fellow%20prisoner%20so%20he%20would%20be%20moved%20to%20a%20preferred%20housing%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreech%20has%20also%20admitted%20to%20killing%20at%20least%2040%20other%20people%2C%20and%20officials%20say%20they%20have%20strong%20evidence%20that%20can%20link%20him%20to%20six%20more%20murders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupporters%20for%20Creech's%20death%20sentence%20commutation%20say%20that%20he%20has%20changed%20from%20his%20serial%20killer%20days%20and%20renewed%20his%20faith%20as%20a%20Christian%20in%201993%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fus-news%2Flaw%2Fthomas-creech-execution-idaho-833a54fb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201998%2C%20he%20married%20the%20mother%20of%20a%20corrections%20officer%20who%20was%20working%20at%20his%20detention%20facility%2C%20per%20the%20WSJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20on%20death%20row%20for%2043%20years%2C%20and%20told%20WSJ%20that%20he%20has%20tried%20to%20help%20mentor%20others%20in%20prison%20since%20undergoing%20a%201993%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAda%20County%20Deputy%20Prosecutor%20Jill%20Longhurst%20in%20January%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fidahocapitalsun.com%2F2024%2F01%2F21%2Femotional-commutation-hearing-held-for-idahos-longest-serving-man-on-death-row%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECreech%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Bcharming%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Blikable%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20that%20he%20was%20still%20the%20%26quot%3Bsociopath%20he's%20always%20been.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreech%20is%20not%20the%20only%20US%20inmate%20to%20be%20saved%20from%20death%20row%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20temporarily%20%E2%80%94%20by%20an%20unsuccessful%20IV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Falva-campbell-inmate-who-survived-execution-try-dies-ohio-prison-n852961%5C%22%20t