outing%20out%20questions%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20run%20for%2055%20days%2C%20Shahjahan%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20serious%20allegations%20levelled%20by%20residents%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20an%20island%20in%20Bengal's%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district.%20The%20Trinamool%20strongman%20and%20his%20aides%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20land%20grab%2C%20extortion%20and%20intimidation.%20Allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20have%20also%20come%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20police%2C%20which%20arrested%20Shahjahan%20yesterday%2C%20has%20said%20a%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20order%20had%20tied%20their%20hands.%20The%20court%20had%20subsequently%20clarified%20that%20it%20has%20not%20stopped%20the%20state%20police%20or%20the%20ED%20or%20CBI%20from%20arresting%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%2C%20senior%20Bengal%20police%20officer%20Supratim%20Sarkar%20questioned%20why%20the%20central%20agency%20did%20not%20arrest%20Shahjahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20from%20the%20ED%20have%20hit%20back%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20pace%20of%20the%20strongman's%20arrest%20shows%20that%20Shahjahan%20was%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20High%20Court%20gives%20a%20clarification%20and%20Shahjahan%20is%20instantly%20arrested.%20This%20proves%20that%20he%20was%20with%20them.%20The%20court%20had%20paused%20action%20in%20one%20case.%20But%20why%20was%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20not%20arrested%20despite%20being%20named%20in%20three%20murder%20cases.%20He%20also%20faced%20a%20non-bailable%20warrant%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20attack%20on%20power%20department%20officials%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20ED%20officer%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20was%20he%20not%20arrested%20despite%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20land%20grab%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20ED%20team%20was%20attacked%20by%20a%20huge%20mob%20on%20January%205%20when%20it%20went%20to%20raid%20Shahjahan's%20house%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20case%20of%20irregularities%20in%20ration%20distribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20information%20that%20there%20was%20a%20huge%20cache%20of%20arms%20and%20cash%20worth%20crores%20at%20his%20home.%20That's%20why%20the%20mob%20attack%20was%20engineered%20and%20Shahjahan%20was%20helped%20to%20flee.%20The%20role%20of%20Bengal%20police%20and%20government%20in%20hiding%20away%20the%20arms%2C%20cash%20and%20Shahjahan's%20phones%20must%20be%20investigated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20official%20said%20custodial%20interrogation%20of%20the%20strongman%20was%20required%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20alleged%20ration%20distribution%20scam%20and%20allegations%20of%20land%20grab.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20watching%20the%20actions%20of%20Bengal%20police.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20fire%20over%20the%20allegations%20against%20Shahjahan%20and%20his%20aides%2C%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20had%20said%20that%20a%20high%20court%20order%20was%20impeding%20the%20state%20police's%20crackdown%20against%20the%20strongman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20High%20Court%20ties%20the%20hands%20of%20state%20administration%20(then)%20what%20can%20be%20done%3F%20After%20the%20January%205%20incident%20-%20when%20it%20was%20claimed%20ED%20officers%20were%20attacked%20-%20the%20central%20agency%20filed%20a%20complaint%20and%20the%20High%20Court%20ordered%20the%20constitution%20of%20a%20SIT%20with%20state%20police%20and%20central%20agencies%2C%26quot%3B%20Trinamool%20MP%20and%20general%20secretary%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAround%2010-12%20days%20later%2C%20ED%20appealed%20for%20stay%20in%20the%20High%20Court.%20The%20plea%20was%20accepted.%20This%20means%20they%20did%20not%20want%20any%20investigation%2C%20arrest%2C%20summons%2C%20or%20interrogation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20The%20Trinamool%20leader%2C%20who%20is%20the%20nephew%20of%20party%20chief%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20had%20insisted%20that%20the%20state%20government%20was%20not%20shielding%20the%20strongman.%20He%20had%20pointed%20to%20the%20arrests%20of%20Shahjahan's%20aides%20Uttam%20Sardar%20and%20Shibu%20Hazra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20later%20clarified%20that%20it%20had%20not%20barred%20the%20state%20police%20from%20arresting%20the%20strongman.%20%26quot%3BWe%20clarify%20there%20is%20no%20stay%20on%20arrest%20in%20any%20proceeding.%20There%20is%20only%20a%20first%20information%20report%20and%20he%20(Shahjahan)%20has%20been%20named%20as%20an%20accused.%20He%20is%20absconding.%20Obviously%20he%20needs%20to%20be%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709188980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fe14mic4o_sheikh-shahjahan_625x300_29_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-shahjahan-sandeshkhali-shahjahan-was-with-bengal-cops-probe-agency-after-strongmans-arrest-5148651%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Clad%20in%20a%20white%20shirt%2C%20white%20trousers%20and%20a%20grey%20jacket%2C%20Sandeshkhali%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20reached%20a%20court%20in%20West%20Bengal%20this%20morning%2C%20hours%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20mob%20attack%20on%20a%20team%20of%20ED%20officials%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-shahjahan-sandeshkhali-shahjahan-was-with-bengal-cops-probe-agency-after-strongmans-arrest-5148651%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-shahjahan-sandeshkhali-shahjahan-was-with-bengal-cops-probe-agency-after-strongmans-arrest-5148651%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-shahjahan-sandeshkhali-shahjahan-was-with-bengal-cops-probe-agency-after-strongmans-arrest-5148651%2Fa