20Sukhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyers%20representing%20these%20disqualified%20MLAs%20called%20the%20move%20illegal%20and%20are%20likely%20to%20challenge%20it%20in%20the%20high%20court.%20Congress%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20that%20the%20move%20would%20be%20vital%20in%20keeping%20its%20remaining%20flock%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20disqualifying%20these%20six%20MLAs%2C%20Sukhu%20invited%20all%20remaining%2034%20MLAs%20of%20the%20party%20for%20a%20breakfast%20meeting%20at%20his%20office-residence%20in%20Shimla%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20further%20defection%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20all%20MLAs%20reached%20in%20time%20for%20breakfast%2C%20Congress%20claimed%20that%20the%20government%20was%20stable%20and%20that%20all%20remaining%20MLAs%20stand%20solid%20with%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20Congress%20observers%20%E2%80%93%20D.K.%20Shivkumar%2C%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%20%E2%80%93%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20sent%20by%20the%20party%20high%20command%20to%20handle%20the%20Himachal%20situation%2C%20were%20also%20present%20in%20the%20meeting.%20They%20interacted%20with%20MLAs%20present%20and%20assured%20them%20that%20concerns%20with%20the%20government%20will%20soon%20be%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20at%20night%2C%20these%20leaders%20also%20appeared%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fpolitics%2Fhimachal-bjp-congress-coup-independents-governor%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3Eplacated%3C%2Fa%3E%20Congress%20MLA%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20at%20least%20temporarily.%20The%20son%20of%20late%20Congress%20CM%20Virbhadra%20Singh%2C%20who%20resigned%20on%20Wednesday%20from%20Sukhu%20cabinet%2C%20had%20cited%20that%20party%20MLAs%20were%20being%20humiliated%20in%20the%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirbhadra%20said%20that%20Congress%20observers%20had%20told%20him%20that%20his%20concerns%20would%20be%20addressed.%20However%2C%20he%20did%20not%20appear%20at%20today%E2%80%99s%20breakfast%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESukhu%20government%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20a%20majority%20mark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20disqualification%20of%20these%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20Congress%20had%20a%20strength%20of%2040%20in%2068-member%20state%20assembly.%20Besides%2C%20it%20enjoyed%20support%20of%20three%20independents%20too.%20The%20remaining%2025%20belonged%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strength%20of%20the%20House%20has%20now%20reduced%20to%2062%20after%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20disqualification%20move%20against%20these%20six%20Congress%20rebels%2C%20with%20magic%20majority%20mark%20currently%20standing%20at%2032.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20current%20situation%2C%20there%20is%20no%20immediate%20danger%20to%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20since%20it%20claims%20to%20enjoy%20the%20support%20of%20the%20remaining%2034%20MLAs%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20danger%20is%20not%20fully%20over%20since%20any%20further%20defections%20in%20the%20party%20may%20spell%20doom%20for%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20and%20trigger%20its%20collapse%20%E2%80%93%20something%20the%20BJP%20is%20eyeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20claims%20that%20their%20Himachal%20government%20is%20safe%20and%20will%20complete%20a%20full%20five%20years%2C%20there%20is%20also%20no%20denying%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20nows%20sits%20on%20the%20fence%20of%20a%20majority%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20already%20claimed%20that%20Sukhu%20government%20days%20are%20numbered%20as%20more%20Congress%20MLAs%20would%20switch%20sides%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnically%20speaking%2C%20BJP%20is%20also%20not%20far%20from%20the%20majority%20mark.%20With%2025%20MLAs%20and%203%20independents%2C%20it%20now%20has%2028%20MLAs%20to%20its%20side%20against%20the%2034%20in%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A170918888400