5C%22%3ERBI%20stops%20onboarding%20of%20new%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22376%5C%22%3EMaterial%20supervisory%20concerns%20observed%20in%20the%20bank%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22132%5C%22%3EOctober%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22209%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frbidocs.rbi.org.in%2Frdocs%2FPressRelease%2FPDFs%2FPR1091BA60EEE8A1E54DF6988011244A0616D7.PDF%5C%22%3ERBI%20imposes%20penalty%20of%20Rs%2053.9%20million%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22376%5C%22%3ENon-compliance%20with%20KYC%2C%20licensing%20requirements%20of%20Payment%20Banks%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22132%5C%22%3EJanuary%2031%2C%202024%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22209%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frbidocs.rbi.org.in%2Frdocs%2FPressRelease%2FPDFs%2FPR1774PPBLBEDADC47266E41F7A65307C63180E2B1.PDF%5C%22%3ERBI%20curbs%20operations%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22376%5C%22%3EPersistent%20non-compliances%20and%20continued%20material%20supervisory%20concerns%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%20Media%20and%20RBI%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%20had%20a%20history%20of%20RBI%20censures%20for%20violations%20pertaining%20to%20onboarding%20of%20customers%2C%20and%20especially%2C%20in%20the%20all-important%20know%20your%20customer%20(KYC)%20guidelines.%20As%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fhow-paytm-payments-bank-came-under-rbi-lens-1000-accounts-linked-to-1-pan-and-more%2Farticleshow%2F107507099.cms%5C%22%3Emedia%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20RBI%20detected%20hundreds%20of%20customer%20accounts%20were%20onboarded%20without%20proper%20documentation%2C%20and%20more%20than%201%2C000%20customers%20were%20reportedly%20linked%20to%20a%20single%20Permanent%20Account%20Number%20(PAN).%20Such%20violations%20suggest%20either%20poor%20operational%20practices%20to%20facilitate%20business%20growth%2C%20or%20more%20ominously%2C%20a%20business%20strategy%20of%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobally%2C%20KYC%20has%20become%20the%20bedrock%20of%20banking%2C%20as%20banks%20must%20have%20comprehensive%20knowledge%20of%20their%20customers%2C%20depositors%20and%20borrowers%20from%20a%20risk%20management%20as%20well%20as%20an%20anti-money%20laundering%20perspective.%20Therefore%2C%20when%20the%20banking%20regulator%20serves%20notice%20for%20violations%2C%20penalises%20and%20even%20takes%20the%20extreme%20step%20of%20stopping%20onboarding%20of%20new%20customers%20(as%20the%20RBI%20did%20with%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20on%20March%2011%2C%202022)%2C%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20must%20take%20notice%20and%20immediately%20address%20the%20concerns%20to%20the%20regulator%E2%80%99s%20satisfaction.%20The%20bank%E2%80%99s%20independent%20directors%2C%20however%2C%20managed%20to%20sleep%20soundly%20through%20all%20the%20noise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%20board%20of%20directors%20from%20FY22%20to%20FY23%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22442%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFY2022%20%E2%80%93%20FY2023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22144%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDate%20of%20Appointment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22131%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDate%20of%20Resignation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22442%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fvijayshekhar%2F%3ForiginalSubdomain%3Din%5C%22%3EVijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%2C%20part-time%20Chairman%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22144%5C%22%3EAugust%2022%2C%202016%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22131%5C%22%3EFebruary%2026%2C%202024%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22442%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheorg.com%2Forg%2Fpaytm-pay