VOOdF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%20Ministry%20of%20National%20Defense%2C%20R.O.C.%20%F0%9F%87%B9%F0%9F%87%BC%20(%40MoNDefense)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMoNDefense%2Fstatus%2F1763045214539899029%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20in%20February%2C%20Taiwan%20has%20detected%20Chinese%20military%20aircraft%20253%20times%20and%20naval%20ships%20150%20times%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Taiwan%20News%20report.%20Since%20September%202020%2C%20China%20has%20intensified%20its%20use%20of%20gray%20zone%20tactics%20by%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20military%20aircraft%20and%20naval%20ships%20operating%20around%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGray%20zone%20tactics%20have%20been%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Beffort%20or%20series%20of%20efforts%20beyond%20steady-state%20deterrence%20and%20assurance%20that%20attempt%20to%20achieve%20one's%20security%20objectives%20without%20resorting%20to%20direct%20and%20sizable%20use%20of%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20Taiwan%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2014%2C%20the%20US%20nominee%20to%20helm%20US%20Indo-Pacific%20Command%2C%20Admiral%20Samuel%20Paparo%2C%20warned%20that%20China%20could%20soon%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20use%20military%20exercises%20to%20conceal%20an%20invasion%20of%20Taiwan%2C%20Taiwan%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmiral%20Paparo%20made%20the%20remarks%20at%20a%20conference%20organised%20by%20the%20Defence%20Innovation%20Unit%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20to%20discuss%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20private%20sector%20can%20collaborate%20with%20the%20US%20military%20in%20leveraging%20emerging%20commercial%20technologies%20to%20strengthen%20America's%20defences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaparo%20touched%20on%20the%20growing%20threat%20by%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20and%20ways%20that%20the%20US%20could%20use%20new%20technologies%20to%20deter%20Beijing.%20The%20US%20Commander%20further%20said%20that%20despite%20economic%2C%20demographic%20woes%20in%20China%2C%20and%20the%20corruption%20scandals%20within%20the%20PLA%2C%20Beijing's%20leadership%20is%20%26quot%3Bundaunted%20in%20their%20ambitions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20these%20ambitions%20include%20the%20world%2C%20the%20West%20Pacific%2C%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bmore%20acutely%20for%20Taiwan%2C%26quot%3B%20Taiwan%20News%20reported.%20According%20to%20Paparo%2C%20the%20PLA%20within%20the%20past%20three%20years%20has%20achieved%20%26quot%3Bstep-level%20changes%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20force%20levels%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bjointness%26quot%3B%20of%20those%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20these%20developments%2C%20along%20with%20PLA%20rehearsals%20demonstrating%20joint%20capabilities%20and%20the%20heightened%20threshold%20of%20warnings%2C%20indicate%20that%20China%20will%20soon%20reach%20a%20point%20at%20which%20it%20will%20have%20sufficient%20forces%20to%20launch%20a%20%26quot%3Bprofound%20military%20operation%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20be%20operated%20%26quot%3Bunder%20a%20fig%20leaf%20of%20exercise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Paparo%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Berosion%20of%20strategic%20operational%20and%20tactical%20warning%20is%20real%26quot%3B%20and%20presents%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20to%20detect%20warning%20signs%20of%20a%20Chinese%20attack.%20He%20said%20that%20this%20could%20hinder%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20US%20military%20to%20be%20properly%20positioned%20to%20support%20allies%20and%20partners%20and%20affect%20its%20readiness%20to%20defend%20Taiwan%20if%20China%20should%20%26quot%3Bdecide%20to%20settle%20matters%20with%20the%20use%20of%20force.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%