%20Putin%20(R)%20and%20North%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20(L)%20visit%20a%20construction%20site%20of%20the%20Angara%20rocket%20launch%20complex%20on%20September%2013%2C%202023%20in%20Tsiolkovsky%2C%20Russia.%3Cp%3EContributor%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESouth%20Korea's%20defense%20minister%20said%20North%20Korea%20has%20been%20exchanging%20arms%20for%20food%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIts%20factories%20are%20mostly%20at%2030%25%20capacity%2C%20but%20the%20ones%20making%20arms%20for%20Russia%20are%20at%20100%25%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENorth%20Korea%20has%20shipped%206%2C700%20containers%20to%20Russia%20since%20August%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korean%20weapons%20factories%20are%20%26quot%3Boperating%20at%20full%20capacity%26quot%3B%20making%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20for%20Russia%2C%20South%20Korean%20Defense%20Minister%20Shin%20Won-sik%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20North%20Korea's%20arms%20factories%20operate%20at%2030%25%20capacity%20due%20to%20shortages%20of%20raw%20materials%20and%20power%2C%20certain%20factories%20are%20operating%20at%20full%20capacity%2C%20which%20primarily%20produces%20weapons%20and%20shells%20for%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shin%20in%20a%20press%20briefing%2C%20per%20a%20translation%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.yna.co.kr%2Fview%2FAEN20240227002800315%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYonhap%20News%20Agency.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShin%20also%20said%20North%20Korea%20has%20provided%206%2C700%20containers%20to%20Russia%20since%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20enough%20cargo%20space%20for%203%20million%20rounds%20of%20152%20mm%20artillery%20shells%20or%20500%2C000%20rounds%20of%20122%20mm%20artillery%20shells%2C%20Shin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20exchange%2C%20Russia%20has%20been%20sending%20North%20Korea%20food%20and%20raw%20materials%20needed%20to%20create%20munitions%2C%20Shin%20said.