lude%20fines%20as%20well%20as%20cancellation%20of%20trade%20licence%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'60%20per%20cent%20Kannada'%20signage%20rule%20is%20set%20to%20be%20implemented%20across%20the%20state%20after%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20brought%20the%20Kannada%20Language%20Comprehensive%20Development%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024.%20The%20legislation%20has%20cleared%20the%20Assembly%20and%20also%20received%20the%20Governor's%20assent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2060%20per%20cent%20signage%20rule%20was%20announced%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20dramatic%20scenes%20in%20Bengaluru%20markets%20over%20the%20language%20row.%20A%20viral%20video%20showed%20leaders%20of%20Karnataka%20Rakshana%20Vedike%20-%20an%20organisation%20pushing%20the%20language%20issue%20-%20were%20seen%20threatening%20shopkeepers%20on%20a%20microphone.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Karnataka.%20The%20Kannadigas%20are%20this%20state's%20pride.%20You%20go%20and%20show%20your%20pride%20in%20your%20state.%20Marwaris%2C%20next%20time%20you%20say%20you%20do%20not%20know%20Kannada%2C%20you%20will%20be%20a%20target%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20leader%20was%20heard%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kannada%20language%20push%20has%20support%20from%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum.%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20earlier%20said%20that%20everyone%20living%20in%20Karnataka%20should%20learn%20Kannada.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20all%20Kannadigas.%20People%20speaking%20different%20languages%20have%20settled%20in%20this%20Kannada%20land%20since%20the%20unification%20of%20Karnataka.%20Everyone%20living%20in%20this%20state%20should%20learn%20to%20speak%20Kannada%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20exist%20in%20states%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20without%20learning%20the%20local%20language%2C%20you%20can%20survive%20in%20Karnataka%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20speak%20Kannada%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20pushed%20for%20wider%20use%20of%20the%20local%20language%20in%20his%20earlier%20term%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20from%20Karnataka%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Prahlad%20Joshi%20has%20also%20backed%20the%20signage%20move.%20Speaking%20to%20NDTV%20after%20some%20Bengaluru%20shops%20were%20vandalised%20by%20members%20of%20pro-Kannada%20groups%20over%20the%20language%20row%2C%20he%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20should%20be%20able%20to%20read%20the%20signs%20and%20not%20everyone%20can%20read%20English.%20What%20is%20the%20harm%20in%20writing%20in%20Kannada%20as%20well%20as%20in%20English%20or%20another%20language%2C%20like%20Hindi%3F%20This%20is%20not%20England.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20has%20been%20violence%20that%20cannot%20be%20approved%20but%20these%20people%20(shopkeepers)%20should%20also%20understand%20the%20sentiment%20and%20the%20necessity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709184060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F2vl2sq2_bengaluru-generic-getty-_625x300_29_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-karnataka-dk-shivakumar-60-kannada-rule-deadline-for-bengaluru-shops-extended-by-2-weeks-5148311%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20row%20over%20Karnataka%20government's%20order%20asking%20shops%20to%20ensure%20at%20least%2060%20per%20cent%20Kannada%20content%20in%20signage%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20today%20said%20the%20deadline%20to%20comply%20to%20the%20rule%20has%20been%20extended%20by%20two%20weeks%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-karnataka-dk-shivakumar-60-kannada-rule-deadline-for-bengaluru-shops-extended-by-2-weeks-5148311%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jharkhand%3A%20At%20Least%20Two%