d%20wash%20their%20clothes%20in%20the%20ocean%2C%20scrub%20them%20with%20hand%20sanitizer%2C%20or%20boil%20them%20in%20the%20cooking%20pot%20to%20keep%20them%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Patel%20said%20the%20production%20team%20has%20a%20second%20%26quot%3Bidentical%20set%26quot%3B%20of%20outfits%20%26quot%3Bin%20case%20something%20happens%20to%20the%20clothes%20that%20you're%20wearing.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can't%20put%20that%20on%20TV%2C%20but%20they'll%20exchange%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20won't%20mention%20who%2C%20but%20there%20were%20several%20people%20in%20our%20cast%20who%20got%20replacement%20clothes%20swapped%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three-time%20contestant%20Malcolm%20Freberg%20said%20he%20lost%20a%20flip-flop%20near%20the%20start%20of%20%26quot%3BSurvivor%3A%20Philippines%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20given%20a%20replacement.%20He%20called%20this%20%26quot%3Ba%20big%20deal%26quot%3B%20because%20he%20might%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20get%20around%20the%20island%20with%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20more%20details%2C%20read%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-uri%3D%5C%2266f44a1794f7af191be48ac67e7006e1%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdo-survivor-players-pick-their-outfits-how-2021-6%5C%22%3E'Survivor'%20players%20reveal%20how%20the%20show%20chooses%20their%20only%20outfit%20and%20what%20it's%20like%20wearing%20it%20for%20up%20to%2039%20days%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EContestants%20can%20also%20request%20a%20new%20pair%20of%20underwear%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20easy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECarbin%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20holes%20in%20my%20underwear%26quot%3B%20and%20asked%20the%20crew%20for%20a%20new%20pair%20but%20was%20initially%20turned%20down.%20She%20said%20she%20got%20a%20replacement%20only%20after%20they%20h