collection%20of%20amounts%20for%20about%202.5%20crores%2C%20with%20out%20issuing%20any%20bonds%20indicates%20that%20the%20said%20amounts%20was%20misappropriated%20for%20their%20self.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20the%20retired%20judge%20said%20that%20he%20paid%20everything%20in%20%E2%80%9Cwhite%E2%80%9D%20(legal%20money).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20asking%20several%20times%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20they%20did%20not%20issue%20the%20bonds%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20told%20the%20news%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709135304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F08223208%2Frupee-g9dbf1131e_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectoral-bonds-andhra-pradesh-high-court-retired-judge-scammed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20complaint%2C%20Varma%20mentioned%20that%20the%20scammers%20claimed%20that%20they%20would%20purchase%20electoral%20bonds%20with%20the%20money%20and%20in%20exchange%20they%20would%20%26quot%3Bplace%20him%20and%20his%20grandchildren%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20US%20decently%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectoral-bonds-andhra-pradesh-high-court-retired-judge-scammed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CIL%20to%20hold%2051%25%20stake%20in%20Rs%2011%2C700%20crore%20coal-to-chemical%20JV%20with%20BHEL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709134346000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F06%2Ffull%2F1699255279-0816.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcil-to-hold-51-stake-in-rs-11-700-crore-coal-to-chemical-jv-with-bhel-124022801087_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20venture%20will%20kick%20off%20with%20the%