%20human%20rights%20violations%E2%80%A6%20We%20must%20never%20tolerate%20or%20ignore%20the%20flagrant%20disregard%20for%20the%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20our%20forebearers%20worked%20so%20arduously%20to%20define%20and%20to%20codify.%20Nor%20should%20we%20ignore%20the%20systemic%20impunity%20with%20which%20it%20is%20perpetrated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Francis%20also%20insisted%20on%20the%20need%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%E2%80%9D%20in%20Gaza%20and%20for%20humanitarian%20corridors%20to%20deliver%20aid%20to%20some%201.5%20million%20homeless%20Palestinians%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20name%20of%20humanity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appeal%20by%20the%20President%20of%20the%20General%20Assembly%20came%20days%20after%20receiving%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20head%20of%20the%20UN%20agency%20for%20Palestinians%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2F%5C%22%3EUNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20warning%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmonumental%20disaster%E2%80%9D%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20amid%20repeated%20Israeli%20calls%20to%20dismantle%20it%20and%20the%20freezing%20of%20%24450%20million%20in%20funding%20by%20dozens%20of%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20implore%C2%A0%20donor%20States%20to%20uphold%20and%20sustain%20their%20contributions%20to%20the%20critical%20funding%20necessary%20for%20UNRWA%20to%20discharge%20its%20mandated%20responsibilities%20to%20the%20Palestinians.%20Even%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20current%20extraordinary%20challenges%2C%20UNRWA%20has%20been%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20indispensable%20lifeline%20of%20support%20to%20the%20Palestinians%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr.%20Francis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146942%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20UN%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709112095000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fupload