eg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frahul-arepaka-1709043428-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frahul-arepaka-1709043428-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frahul-arepaka-1709043428-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frahul-arepaka-1709043428-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frahul-arepaka-1709043428-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343359%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERahul%20Arepaka%2C%20Founder%2C%20Harvested%20Robotics%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20methods%20of%20weed%20removal%20involve%20the%20use%20of%20weedicides%20or%20herbicides%2C%20which%20are%20chemicals%20sprayed%20on%20the%20field%20to%20eliminate%20weeds.%20Though%20this%20is%20effective%2C%20it%20has%20a%20long-term%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20environment%20and%20the%20health%20of%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELearning%20about%20this%20problem%20prompted%20Rahul%20Arepaka%2C%20an%20engineering%20student%20at%20Mahindra%20University%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20to%20develop%20a%20solution.%20He%20built%20an%20AI-powered%20laser-weeding%20implement%20called%20%E2%80%98Rakshak%E2%80%99%20through%20his%20company%2C%20Harvested%20Robotics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20farmer%20spends%20almost%20Rs%2015%2C000%20for%20weeding%2C%20which%20has%20to%20be%20done%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20times%20during%20an%20entire%20season.%20So%20the%20total%20cost%20sums%20up%20to%20almost%20Rs%2060%2C000.%20The%20other%20option%20is%20using%20chemicals%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20solution%20that%20is%20good%20for%20the%20farmer%20as%20well%20as%20the%20planet%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%