to%20our%20homes.%20It%20was%20a%20period%20when%20families%20came%20together%20to%20cook%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20tackle%20household%20chores%20collectively.%20Even%20the%20children%2C%20with%20their%20newfound%20time%20at%20home%2C%20lent%20a%20helping%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20scene%20unfolded%20at%20Simran%20Khara%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Delhi.%20The%2042-year-old%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20then%20five-year-old%20daughter%2C%20spent%20much%20of%20their%20time%20on%20household%20chores.%20After%20a%20few%20days%2C%20Simran%20started%20studying%20the%20labels%20of%20the%20dishwashing%20and%20floor%20cleaning%20products%20she%20was%20using%20at%20home.%20She%20recognised%20the%20presence%20of%20harmful%20chemicals%20in%20these%20cleaners%2C%20which%20posed%20risks%20to%20her%20daughter%20and%20even%20the%20surfaces%20they%20cleaned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20longer%20at%20ease%20with%20her%20daughter%20participating%20in%20cleaning%20activities%20due%20to%20the%20potential%20exposure%20to%20these%20toxic%20chemicals%2C%20Simran%2C%20a%20concerned%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20MBA%20graduate%20with%2014%20years%20of%20corporate%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20resolved%20to%20develop%20a%20line%20of%20eco-friendly%20home%20cleaners%20that%20would%20prioritise%20child%20and%20pet%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20research%2C%20Simran%20Khara%2C%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20Juggernaut%20Books%2C%20launched%20Koparo%20Clean%20in%20February%202021.%20Koparo%20Clean%20is%20a%20home-care%20product%20brandboasting%20of%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%E2%80%9D%20formulations%20crafted%20from%20plant-based%20ingredients%20such%20as%20coconuts%20(%3Cem%3Ekopra%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20entrepreneurial%20journey%20gained%20national%20attention%20when%20she%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20Season%203%2C%20where%20she%20secured%20a%20substantial%20investment%20of%20Rs%2070%20lakh%20from%20%E2%80%98Sharks%E2%80%99%20Vineeta%20Sin