tle%22%3A%22900%20Kids%20Are%20Now%20Able%20to%20Hear%2C%20Thanks%20to%20Support%20From%20This%20Life-Changing%20Initiative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20child%20is%20born%2C%20parents%20celebrate%20each%20milestone%20in%20their%20life%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20first%20rollover%20to%20crawling%20and%20walking.%20Another%20significant%20moment%20every%20parent%20eagerly%20awaits%20is%20their%20baby%E2%80%99s%20first%20word.%20Each%20child%20develops%20uniquely%2C%20hitting%20these%20milestones%20at%20different%20times.%20However%2C%20parents%20need%20to%20remain%20attentive%20and%20raise%20concerns%20if%20these%20milestones%20are%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334578%2Fcoda-child-of-deaf-adult-indian-sign-language-isl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHearing%2C%20an%20invisible%20aspect%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20goes%20unnoticed%20until%20the%20child%20begins%20to%20speak%20or%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20A%20child%20who%20is%20not%20able%20to%20hear%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20respond%20to%20noises%20or%20their%20name%2C%20and%20won%E2%80%99t%20start%20babbling%20and%20trying%20to%20imitate%20sounds%20by%20six%20to%20eight%20months.%20If%20parents%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20such%20childhood%20milestones%20they%20may%20not%20become%20aware%20of%20potential%20hearing%20issues%20until%20around%20the%20time%20the%20child%20reaches%20two%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20advancements%20in%20healthcare%20and%20technology%2C%20newborn%20hearing%20screenings%20can%20now%20detect%20hearing%20loss%20much%20before%20even%20the%20earliest%20milestones-based%20diagnosis.%20These%20screenings%20aid%20in%20the%20early%20detection%20of%20hearing%20problems%2C%20allowing%20for%20follow-up%20consultations%20with%20paediatricians%20within%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20first%20two%20to%20three%20months%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20estimates%20that%20there%20are%2063%20million%20people%20in%20India%20who%20suffer%20from%20significant%20auditory%20impairment.%20It%20further%20notes%20that%20up%20to%20five%20out%20of%20every%201%2C000%20babies%20are%20born%20with%20hearing%20loss%20or%20acquire%20it%20soon%20after%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20key%20to%20effective%20management%20of%20hearing%20loss%20is%20early%20identification%20and%20prompt%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20experiencing%20mild%20to%20moderate%20hearing%20loss%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F63445%2Fhearing-impairments-balavidyalaya-school-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefit%20from%20hearing%20aids%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20those%20with%20profound%20hearing%20loss%2C%20Cochlear%20Implants%20(CI)%20offer%20a%20solution.%20These%20electronic%20devices%20serve%20to%20replace%20the%20function%20of%20the%20damaged%20inner%20ear%2C%20facilitating%20the%20sense%20of%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20enables%20children%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20auditory%20world%20and%20lead%20lives%20similar%20to%20other%20children%20in%20every%20aspect.%20However%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20Cochlear%20Implant%20(CI)%20surgery%20is%20expensive%20for%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20population%20in%20India.%20To%20assist%20children%20in%20regaining%20their%20hearing%20abilities%20and%20leading%20fulfilling%20lives%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341889%2Fhans-foundation-bal-aarogya-karyakram-childhood-cancer-paediatric-oncology-leukaemia-lymphoma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20%3C%2Fa%3E(THF)%20runs%20the%20Cochlear%20Implant%20Programme.%20Through%20this%