In%20India%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20estimated%20that%20every%20ninth%20person%20may%20develop%20cancer%20in%20their%20lifetime.%20With%20cancer%20cases%20projected%20to%20rise%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10231735%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E15%20lakh%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%202025%2C%20patients%20often%20hesitate%20to%20undergo%20life-saving%20chemotherapy%20due%20to%20concerns%20about%20hair%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChemotherapy%2C%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20cancer%20treatment%2C%20not%20only%20targets%20cancer%20cells%20but%20also%20damages%20rapidly%20dividing%20healthy%20cells%2C%20including%20hair%20follicles.%20Studies%20indicate%20that%20approximately%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F37185388%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DChemotherapy%2520causes%2520substantial%2520thinning%2520or%2Cinterventional%2520options%2520have%2520been%2520limited.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E65%20percent%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20patients%20experience%20significant%20hair%20thinning%20or%20loss%20as%20a%20result%20of%20chemotherapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20problem%20has%20been%20persistent%20since%20the%20advent%20of%20chemotherapy.%20There%20is%20an%20immense%20stigma%20attached%20to%20hair%20loss%20and%20cancer.%20If%20a%20woman%20goes%20bald%20suddenly%2C%20then%20people%20are%20quick%20to%20gossip%20about%20it.%20Besides%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20social%20or%20personal%20obligations%20where%20people%20wish%20to%20retain%20hair%20%E2%80%94%20from%20keeping%20the%20condition%20private%20from%20society%20to%20wanting%20a%20sense%20of%20normalcy%20for%20their%20family%20to%20name%20a%20few%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raghuveer%20Surupa%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20patient%20has%20an%20upcoming%20wedding%20or%20big%20event%2C%20then%20also%20they%20tend%20to%20delay%20their%20chemotherapies.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20people%20delay%20life-saving%20treatment%20for%20the%20fear%20of%20hair%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-1-1708521986.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raghuveer%20designed%20a%20universal%20cap%20to%20protect%20hair%20follicles%20from%20chemotherapy%20damage.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-1-1708521986.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-1-1708521986-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-1-1708521986-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-1-1708521986-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-1-1708521986-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342787%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERaghuveer%20designed%20a%20universal%20cap%20to%20protect%20hair%20follicles%20from%20chemotherapy%20damage.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20this%20unavoidable%20problem%2C%20Raghuveer%20has%20developed%20a%20unique%20scalp%20cooling%20system%20that%20alleviates%20the%20trauma%20of%20chemotherapy-induced%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F21121%2Fnatural-hair-wigs-cancer-patients-chennai-tangled%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehair%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Currently%2C%20his%20innovation%20%E2%80%98Eva%20Scalp%20Cooling%20System%E2%80%99%20is%20installed%20in%2018%20hospitals%20across%20Telangana%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Delhi.%20He%20says%20more%20than%203%2C000%20successful%20sessions%20have%20been%20conducted%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20Raghuveer%20to%20understand%20more%20about%20the%20novel%20device%20and%20how%20it%20can%20solve%20one%20of%20chemotherapy%E2%80%99s%20most%20challenging%20side%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20scalp%20cooling%20mechanism%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20engineer%20by%20education%2C%20Raghuveer%20pursued%20his%20higher%20education%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%2C%20Ranchi.%20In%202013%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315492%2Fvadodara-pragmatech-healthcare-solutions-cervicheck-kits-detect-cervical-cancer-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epharmaceutical%20company%20%3C%2Fa%3EPfizer%20and%20later%20worked%20with%20Roche%20where%20he%20was%20a%20launch%20lead%20for%20the%20breast%20cancer%20drug%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20his%20work%20experience%20in%20oncology%2C%20he%20founded%20his%20own%20startup%20%E2%80%98Dignite%E2%80%99%20for%20cancer%20care.%20Although%20it%20did%20not%20succeed%2C%20Raghuveer%20learnt%20about%20the%20urgency%20of%20handling%20the%20side%20effects%20of%20chemotherapies%20%E2%80%94%20hair%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-2-1708521951.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raghuveer%20has%20developed%20a%20unique%20scalp%20cooling%20system%20that%20alleviates%20the%20trauma%20of%20chemotherapy-induced%20hair%20loss.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-2-1708521951.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-2-1708521951-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-2-1708521951-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-2-1708521951-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-2-1708521951-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERaghuveer%20has%20developed%20a%20unique%20scalp%20cooling%20system%20that%20alleviates%20the%20trauma%20of%20chemotherapy-induced%20hair%20loss.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remembered%20the%20experience%20of%20my%20aunt%20when%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ovarian%20cancer.%20I%20saw%20her%20losing%20confidence%20and%20being%20unable%20to%20get%20by%20with%20her%20life.%20That%20really%20triggered%20me.%20I%20started%20looking%20for%20solutions%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20came%20across%20the%20scalp%20cooling%20method%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%2034-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20availability%20of%20scalp%20cooling%20devices%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20company%20had%20made%20silicon-based%20caps%20that%20come%20in%20three%20different%20sizes%20%E2%80%94%20small%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20large.%20The%20disadvantage%20of%20such%20caps%20is%20that%20they%20cannot%20fit%20all%20kinds%20of%20scalps%20perfectly%2C%20as%20scalps%20have%20a%20very%20complicated%20anatomical%20structure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChemotherapy%20destroys%20all%20fast-growing%20cells%20like%20cancerous%20tumours.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20it%20also%20destroys%20fast-growing%20hair%20follicles%20as%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20differentiate%20between%20healthy%20and%20cancerous%20cells.%20So%2C%20if%20the%20cap%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20fit%20properly%2C%20then%20the%20entire%20scalp%20will%20not%20be%20cooled%2C%20causing%20high%20chances%20of%20hair%20loss%20in%20that%20area.%20This%20destroys%20the%20main%20purpose%20of%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Raghuveer%20decided%20to%20design%20a%20cap%20that%20could%20accommodate%20all%20head%20sizes.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20launched%20his%20company%20Stemtech%20Medical%20Devices%20and%20innovated%20%E2%80%98Eva%20Scalp%20Cooling%20System%E2%80%99%20where%20a%20universal%20cap%20was%20designed%20to%20protect%20hair%20follicles%20from%20chemotherapy%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%20his%20innovation%20%E2%80%98Eva%20Scalp%20Cooling%20System%E2%80%99%20is%20installed%20in%2018%20hospitals.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-3-1708522017-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Currently%2C%20his%20innovation%20%E2%80%98Eva%20Scalp%20Cooling%20System%E2%80%99%20is%20installed%20in%2018%20hospitals.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20design%20was%20inspired%20by%20a%20lotus%20or%20a%20crown.%20Just%20like%20they%20can%20be%20entirely%20closed%2C%20our%20cap%20is%20wrapped%20around%20the%20head%20of%20the%20patient%2C%20and%20the%20cap%20can%20be%20adjusted%20using%20the%20velcro%20as%20per%20the%20need%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghuveer%20informs%20that%20a%20patient%20needs%20to%20wear%20this%20cap%2030%20minutes%20before%20the%20chemotherapy%20infusion%2C%20during%20chemotherapy%20infusion%2C%20and%20between%2030%20minutes%20and%20two%20hours%20post-chemotherapy.%20The%20device%20reduces%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20scalp%20from%2035%20to%2016%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20on%20the%20device%2C%20Raghuveer%20also%20focussed%20on%20reducing%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20device.%20%E2%80%9COur%20competitors%20charge%20about%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20for%20their%20device.%20We%20reduced%20the%20cost%20drastically%20so%20that%20patients%20in%20developing%20countries%20could%20also%20afford%20this%20care.%20Hospitals%20can%20buy%20our%20device%20for%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%2013%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2016%20lakh%20depending%20on%20the%20variant%20of%20the%20device.%20The%20hospitals%20thereafter%20charge%20between%20Rs%201%2C500%20and%20Rs%204%2C000%20per%20patient%20per%20session%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReceived%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20Investment%20in%20Shark%20Tank%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghuveer%20says%20his%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20patients%20can%20get%20through%20the%20therapy%20without%20using%20a%20wig%20or%20a%20scarf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%